response: To a dark place this line of thought will carry us. Great care we must take.
The greatest teacher, failure is.
That is why you fail.
Into exile, I must go. *Failed*, I have.
How embarrassing. How embarrassing.
Until the time is right, disappear, we will.
May the Force be with you!
Good-bye. Miss you I will.
Weapons do not win battles. Your mind, powerful it is.
We're keepers of the peace, not soldiers.
Wars not make one great.
Doubt in battle, there cannot be.  Belief, there must be.  Belief, in the Force.  Reach for it, you will.
Good relations with the Wookiees, I have.

Don't think... feel... be as one
with the Force. Help you, it will.
Attachment leads to jealousy. The shadow of greed, that is.

Much harder to answer, that
question is.
Do not assume anything: clear your mind must be.
Always more questions than answers, there are.
Infinitely more ways there are to reach a goal. Try them all you should.
Rage the true enemy is.
Defeat the rage that burns in him, and he is your enemy no longer.
Powerful you have become, the dark side I sense in you.
Once you start down the dark path, forever will it dominate your destiny.
Anger, fear, aggression. The dark side are they. Easily they flow, quick to join you in a fight.
Told you I did. Reckless he is. Matters are worse.
Heeded my words not, did you?
Defiance, I sense in you. Need that, you do not.
If into the security recordings you go, only pain will you find.
Hard to see, the dark side is.
The shroud of the dark side has fallen. The fear of loss is a path to the Dark Side.
Fear is the path to the Dark Side. Fear leads to anger. Anger leads to hate, hate leads to sufferings.
Impossible to see the future is.
Careful you must be when sensing the future.
A decision is yours alone to make. Yet remember you should that you make it also for the silent ones who stand at your shoulder.
Twilight is upon me, soon night must fall. That is the way of things. The way of the Force.
Not if anything I have to say about it!
Death is a natural part of life. Rejoice for those around you who transform into the Force.
Size matters not. For my ally is the Force, and a powerful ally it is.
Judge me by my size, do you? And well you should not.
It brings warm feeling to my heart.
When nine hundred years old you reach, look as good, you will not, hm?
Look I so old to young eyes?
Sick have I become, old and weak.
More happening there than has been revealed, I feel.
Ah, strong am I with the Force, but not that strong.
Soon will I rest, yes, forever sleep. Earned it I have.
Rest I need. Yes, rest.

Still looking to the horizon.
Never here, huh?
The need under your nose.
Quickly and decisively we should proceed.

Patience. For the Jedi,
it is time to eat as well.
How you get so big, eating food of this kind?

Time, it is.
For you to look at a pile of old books...
Careful timing we will need.

Gather
round the map reader. Find lost planet, we will try...
Truly wonderful, the mind of a child is.
The Dark Side clouds everything.
Looking? Found someone you have, eh?
I mean you no harm. I am wondering, why are you here?

We are what they grow beyond.
That is the true burden
of all masters.
No more training, do you require. Already know you that which you need.
My own counsel will I keep on who is to be trained.
Incomplete was your training. Not ready for the burden were you.
See through you, we can.
He was seduced by the dark side of the Force.
What I told you was true, from a certain point of view.
